{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/welcome-the-first-heavy-snow/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"机知县急流津","author":"lee-ping"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"afc080dc-c7ee-5c39-869c-d54e460c0c84","html":"<p>今天是元宵节，伴随着它的到来假期也快结束了。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/8e1fc/the-lantern-festival.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 42.567567567567565%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"元宵佳节\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/1c72d/the-lantern-festival.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/a80bd/the-lantern-festival.jpg 148w,\n/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/1c91a/the-lantern-festival.jpg 295w,\n/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/1c72d/the-lantern-festival.jpg 590w,\n/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/a8a14/the-lantern-festival.jpg 885w,\n/static/35c053953410ccf55906311986e3b8bb/8e1fc/the-lantern-festival.jpg 900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>今年，新型冠状病毒在武汉爆发，让很多人因此失去了宝贵的生命，多少医务工作者也因此在新春佳节失去与家人团聚的机会而不得不夜以继日的和病毒作斗争。</p>\n<p>就在我们这儿清净、祥和的小村庄里，也下起了多年未见得雪花，它比任何一年都下的那么大，雪花漫天飞舞，堆成厚厚外层。</p>\n<p>从家里冲出去，没想到在河边有人在钓鱼，旁边搂起篝火，虽在雪地里，但倍感温暖。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/644c5/snow-fishing.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"雪地独钓\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/1c72d/snow-fishing.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/a80bd/snow-fishing.jpg 148w,\n/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/1c91a/snow-fishing.jpg 295w,\n/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/1c72d/snow-fishing.jpg 590w,\n/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/a8a14/snow-fishing.jpg 885w,\n/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/fbd2c/snow-fishing.jpg 1180w,\n/static/d0c620e6ba71b4e66fcac8d68cc03d82/644c5/snow-fishing.jpg 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>我怀着好奇冲动的心情在雪地里跋涉，在高地拍下了雪中的县城。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/644c5/snowy-county.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"雪城\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/1c72d/snowy-county.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/a80bd/snowy-county.jpg 148w,\n/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/1c91a/snowy-county.jpg 295w,\n/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/1c72d/snowy-county.jpg 590w,\n/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/a8a14/snowy-county.jpg 885w,\n/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/fbd2c/snowy-county.jpg 1180w,\n/static/8a6035571c9de5aa86c4508e4907f1f5/644c5/snowy-county.jpg 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"迎接第一场大雪","date":"February 08, 2020","spoiler":"大雪飘飘，琉璃时间雪白红梅","cta":null},"fields":{"slug":"/welcome-the-first-heavy-snow/","langKey":"zh-hans"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/welcome-the-first-heavy-snow/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/five-core-sql-statements/","langKey":"zh-hans","directoryName":"five-core-sql-statements","maybeAbsoluteLinks":["/oracles-apex/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"5个核心sql语句"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/question-about-back-to-school/","langKey":"zh-hans","directoryName":"question-about-back-to-school","maybeAbsoluteLinks":[]},"frontmatter":{"title":"回到升学的问题上"}},"translations":[],"translatedLinks":[]}}}